31
00:02:46,960 --> 00:02:47,880
Fanlu.

32
00:02:50,600 --> 00:02:51,880
Jangan berpikir terlalu banyak.

33
00:02:52,839 --> 00:02:53,960
Kau tenang saja.

34
00:02:54,960 --> 00:02:56,479
Tak peduli seperti apa hasilnya,

35
00:02:57,520 --> 00:02:59,000
