36
00:03:00,039 --> 00:03:01,679
sampai kau sembuh.

37
00:03:03,399 --> 00:03:04,399
Jadi,

38
00:03:05,199 --> 00:03:06,600
kau jangan merasa tertekan.

39
00:03:07,839 --> 00:03:09,039
Tidurlah dengan nyenyak.

40
00:03:10,000 --> 00:03:12,839
Besok matahari tetap akan terbit.

41
