Ayah.

44
00:04:01,000 --> 00:04:01,920
Fanlu sudah tidur?

45
00:04:02,920 --> 00:04:03,880
Sudah tidur.

46
00:04:04,440 --> 00:04:05,880
Sudah malam. Kau cepat tidur juga.

47
00:04:06,079 --> 00:04:07,040
Dua hari ini…

48
00:04:07,279 --> 00:04:09,399
