49
00:04:10,720 --> 00:04:11,679
Sudah.

50
00:04:12,519 --> 00:04:13,359
Kalau begitu,

51
00:04:13,600 --> 00:04:15,279
apa dia mengatakan sesuatu padamu?

52
00:04:19,640 --> 00:04:20,559
Xiangyuan,

53
00:04:20,839 --> 00:04:22,440
Yuzheng sudah kembali ke Yutian.

54
00:04:23,679 --> 00:04:25,320
Yutian selain perlu
mendorong pembangunan…

55
00:04:25,320 --> 00:04:26,480
proyek Kota Hiburan,

56
00:04:26,760 --> 00:04:28,760
juga harus melakukan perubahan besar.

57
00:04:28,959 --> 00:04:30,839
Sekarang Yutian
sangat membutuhkan orang.

58
00:04:32,000 --> 00:04:33,279
Ayah harap…

59
00:04:34,359 --> 00:04:36,119
kau bisa melepaskan beban di hatimu…

60
00:04:36,880 --> 00:04:38,640
dan bekerja dengan tekun.

61
00:04:40,559 --> 00:04:41,320
Ayah.

62
00:04:42,519 --> 00:04:43,880
Aku juga ingin bekerja dengan tekun,

63
00:04:45,160 --> 00:04:46,440
tapi Lei Yuzheng sudah pulang,

64
00:04:47,679 --> 00:04:49,040
apa menurut Ayah
dia akan membiarkanku tinggal?

65
00:04:49,440 --> 00:04:50,320
Xiangyuan.

66
00:04:51,119 --> 00:04:52,559
Aku paham kekhawatiranmu.

67
00:04:52,839 --> 00:04:55,279
Jika kau merasa
tidak bisa bertahan di Yutian,

68
00:04:55,839 --> 00:04:57,079
kau datang ke Xinsheng saja.

69
00:04:57,359 --> 00:04:58,600
Kau juga familier…

70
00:04:58,839 --> 00:04:59,880
dengan bisnis keluarga sendiri.

71
00:05:00,119 --> 00:05:01,239
Jika ada ide,

72
00:05:01,519 --> 00:05:03,079
kau juga bisa gampang mewujudkannya.

73
00:05:11,720 --> 00:05:12,519
Ayah,

74
00:05:13,920 --> 00:05:15,320
aku belum bisa menyetujui Ayah sekarang.

75
00:05:18,079 --> 00:05:18,959
Xiangyuan.

76
00:05:19,880 --> 00:05:23,000
Apa kau masih mengkhawatirkan hal itu?

77
00:05:25,320 --> 00:05:27,000
Jika kau sungkan untuk mengatakannya,

78
00:05:27,720 --> 00:05:28,640
aku bisa mewakilimu…

79
00:05:28,799 --> 00:05:30,200
untuk meminta Lei Yuzheng memaafkanmu.

80
00:05:30,799 --> 00:05:31,760
Ayah.

81
00:05:31,959 --> 00:05:33,119
Jangan begini.

82
00:05:35,279 --> 00:05:36,320
Dalam keadaan sekarang,

83
00:05:37,079 --> 00:05:38,600
aku pasrah saja menerima…

84
00:05:39,160 --> 00:05:40,279
tindakan apapun dari Lei Yuzheng.

85
00:05:40,480 --> 00:05:40,839
Tapi…

86
00:05:41,040 --> 00:05:41,839
Ayah.

87
00:05:42,959 --> 00:05:44,480
Besok Fanlu harus
melakukan pemeriksaan ulang.

88
00:05:44,920 --> 00:05:46,239
Istirahatlah lebih awal.

89
00:05:51,559 --> 00:05:52,239
Siqi.

90
00:05:53,760 --> 00:05:55,880
Kau kenapa? Lemas sekali.

91
00:05:58,959 --> 00:06:00,359
